      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 47.3 - 老子 47.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>其知彌少。是以聖人不行而知，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The farther that one goes out (from himself), the less he knows. Therefore the sages got their knowledge without travelling;</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
